                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d537">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        Minister <persName type="to">Sherrill</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1910-07-14">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 14, 1910</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>For your information and repetition to the embassy at Petropolis, I quote the
                    following telegram sent yesterday to the legation at Quito: [See quoted portion
                    of telegram of July 13 to Minister Fox.]</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Wilson.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
